<color=Gold><b>Verdant Guardian</b></color>

<color=Red>(PRESTIGE CLASS: This class is not available at character creation and must be unlocked by meeting special requirements, listed below.)</color>

The verdant guardian is the final defender of the forest. Since most verdant guardians have little use for civilization, they tend to be loners, watching the years pass by from their groves and treasured forests. Adventuring verdant guardians are rare, but those who do exist are marvelous to behold.

<color=Gold>Requirements:</color>

<b>Alignment:</b> Any nonevil.
<b>Class:</b> Ranger 11.
<b>Prohibited Class:</b> Blightlord.
<b>Skills:</b> Heal 8, Survival 8.

