- <b>Hit Die:</b> d8
- <b>Base Attack Bonus:</b> High.
- <b>High Saves:</b> Fort, Will.
- <b>Weapon Proficiencies:</b> None.
- <b>Armor Proficiencies:</b> None.
- <b>Skill Points:</b> 4 + Int modifier.
- <b>Class Skills:</b> Craft Alchemy, Craft Armor, Craft Weapon, Concentration, Diplomacy, Heal, Hide, Listen, Lore, Move Silently, Parry, Spellcraft, Survival, and Tumble.

